MALACAÑANG MANILA

PROCLAMATION NO. 1378

RESERVING CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN BARANGAY FATIMA, MUNICIPALITY OF PANTABANGAN, PROVINCE OF NUEVA ECIJA, ISLAND OF LUZON FOR THE USE OF THE NATIONAL POWER CORPORATION (NPC)

Upon the recommendation of the Secretary of the Department of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale and settlement and reserved for the use of NPC, subject to final ground survey and private rights, if any there be, certain parcels of land of the public domain situated in Barangay Fatima, Municipality of Pantabangan, Province of Nueva Ecija and more particularly described as follows:

